Lassie Lou Ahern https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lassie_Lou_Ahern 0 Lassie Lou Ahern (June 25, 1920 – February 15, 2018) was an American actress. She was best known for her recurring appearances in the Our Gang films. Ahern was also known for her role as Little Harry in the 1927 silent film Uncle Tom's Cabin.
